==English==
===Etymology===
[[Image:Squared-circle_postmark_1890.jpg|thumb|right|A postmark from 1890.]]
Compound of [[post]] + [[mark]].

===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-postmark.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Noun===
'''postmark'''
#A [[marking]] marking made on a [[letter]], [[package]], [[postcard]] or the like indicating the date and time that the item was delivered into the care of the postal service.  Often, the postmark also [[cancel]]s the stamp or indicates that it has been used.